import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
import "bootstrap"

import { createApp } from 'vue'

import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'

import App from './App.vue'

import InicioPage from '@/pages/InicioPage.vue'
import HotelesVer from '@/pages/VerHtl.vue'
import HotelesCrear from '@/pages/HotelesCrear.vue'
import HabitacionesTipo from '@/pages/HabitacionesTipo.vue'
import AcomodacionesHotel from '@/pages/AcomodacionesHotel.vue'


const router = createRouter({
    history: createWebHistory(),
    routes: [
        {patch: '/', name:'InicioPage', component: InicioPage},
        {patch: '/Crear', name:'HotelesCrear', component: HotelesCrear},
        {patch: '@/pages/VerHtl.vue', name:'HoHotelesVerme', component: HotelesVer},
        {patch: '/Tipo', name:'HabitacionesTipo', component: HabitacionesTipo},
        {patch: '/AcomodaHotel', name:'AcomodacionesHotel', component: AcomodacionesHotel},
    ]
})


createApp(App)
.use(router)
.mount('#app')
